  <brief_title>Should Colon or Non-colon Originated Lesions be Distinguished?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Acute Lower Gastrointestinal Dysfunction in Critical Care Patients: Should Colon or Non-colon Originated Lesions be Distinguished?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
