  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective study was designed to compare the difference of effects of conventional
      treatment, medicine intervention, endoscopic therapy, and surgery between colon originated
      and non-colon originated ALGID in critical patients, in order to alert doctors to differ the
      treatment of the two ALGID and provide basis for treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
